				"description": "### Get Room Types\n\nThis endpoint retrieves a list of room types.\n\n#### Response\n\nThe response returns a JSON object with the following properties:\n\n- `message` (string): A message related to the response.\n    \n- `results` (array): An array of room type objects with the following properties:\n    - `referenceNumber` (string): The reference number of the room type.\n        \n    - `name` (string): The name of the room type.\n        \n    - `description` (string): The description of the room type.\n        \n    - `capacity` (integer): The capacity of the room type.\n        \n- `code` (integer): A code related to the response.\n    \n- `error` (boolean): Indicates if an error occurred.\n    \n\n#### JSON Schema\n\n``` json\n{\n  \"type\": \"object\",\n  \"properties\": {\n    \"message\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n    \"results\": {\n      \"type\": \"array\",\n      \"items\": {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"referenceNumber\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n          \"name\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n          \"description\": { \"type\": \"string\" },\n          \"capacity\": { \"type\": \"integer\" }\n        }\n      }\n    },\n    \"code\": { \"type\": \"integer\" },\n    \"error\": { \"type\": \"boolean\" }\n  }\n}\n\n ```"
